@TradersMastery @SirBraden1996 Not really, their post was around “smart homes and personal assistants” without one mention of openclaw. Openclaw variants were released after their post.

People can be long AXT years ago but it’s materially different when there’s a new catalyst. 

Just because there’s a vague ticker mention earlier on doesn’t mean they got the catalyst correct and it’s unfortunate people try to claim credit for what happens later.

